# convert English text into simple XML
# marking.m.elly
#

#  ******** warning *********
#  the ’ below is a wildcard!
#  (it will also match a ')

&@’ll -> \\1 will
&@’re -> \\1 are
can’t -> cannot
won’t -> will not
&@n’t -> \\1 not
&@’ve -> \\1 have
i’m   -> i am
he’s  -> he hvbe
she’s -> she hvbe
it’s  -> it behv
here’s  -> here is
@here’s -> \\1here is
let’s   -> let us
who’s   -> who hvbe
that's -> tht is
that’s -> tht is

mean_that’s -> mean tht is

&@’d    -> \\1 'd
