1_another -> one another

,_@&@ing_that  ->  ,\\s\\2ing that
,"_@&@ing_that -> ",\\s\\2ing that
,”_@&@ing_that -> ",\\s\\2ing that

._._. -> …
...   -> …

is_what -> is cjwhat
go_-s_that -> go -s tht

##&#_k -> \\1_K

!._#*  -> \\1+\\3
no._&# -> no++\\2

approx. -> about
,_lit.  -> , litx

1_is_a_&@ -> x1x is a \\4
